本一致。 同时，按照《企业会计准则》和公司会计政策的相关规定，基于谨慎性原则，公司对存在减值迹象的门店计提了资产减值准备，对提前闭店无法收回的租赁押金计提了相应的坏账准备。上述事项对报告期净利润表现均产生了较大影响，公司归属于上市公司股东的净利润同比下滑 90.54%。 迪阿股份透露，报告期内，公司主动调整渠道策略，关闭了 184 家门店。其中，一季度闭店 9 家，二季度闭店 18 家，三季度闭店 86 家，四季度闭店 71 家。「一生只送一人」，知名珠宝品牌卖不动了？一年闭店 184 家，去年净利润大跌超 90%！ | 每经网"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-1733e3fe820d1a7173c73b9f48d87922_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "114 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/654619792"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IsbqgwZ+4z+wBEAMaCTEwNzc0ODkxMyC99MOxBjAAODFABXIJNjU0NjE5NzkyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "6_1714558902.490753", "card_id": "Q_650631374", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 89}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "《如懿传》中的经典梗「懿症」症状为何？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-8d4fd9f0498587a68aecb3775c63fc69_xl.jpg?source=57bbeac9"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "85 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/650631374"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIsbqgwZ+4z+wBEAMaCTEwNjg2MjU2NSCFiZawBjAAONgBQAZyCTY1MDYzMTM3NHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "7_1714558902.491030", "card_id": "Q_654001701", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 30}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何评价杨幂、